      "type": "lab.html.Form",
      "content": "\u003Cheader\u003E\n  \u003Ch1\u003EWelcome to the Fire Safety Sign Search Task\u003C\u002Fh1\u003E\n\u003C\u002Fheader\u003E\n\n\u003Cmain class=\"content-vertical-center content-horizontal-center\"\u003E\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"w-m text-justify\"\u003E\n    \u003Cp\u003EYou will see a grid of symbols.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003Cp\u003EYour task is to find the Fire Safety Sign as quickly as possible.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003Cp\u003EClick on the fire safety sign when you see it.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n    \u003Cp\u003EYou will first complete a short practice trial.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n  \u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\n\u003C\u002Fmain\u003E\n\n\u003Cfooter class=\"content-horizontal-right\"\u003E\n  \u003Cbutton id=\"continue\"\u003EContinue &rarr;\u003C\u002Fbutton\u003E\n\u003C\u002Ffooter\u003E",
